headline: FormFactor, onsemi, Sensata Technologies, Vishay Intertechnology, and Nova Shares Skyrocket, What You Need To Know
summary: A number of stocks jumped in the afternoon session after a broad rally in the semiconductor sector kicked off the new year, driven by continued investor enthusiasm for artificial intelligence (AI).
